data.text:
Sunday, January 21, 12:00 PM EDT - on Zoom and in person @ the Palestine Museum US, 1764 Litchffield Trnpk, Woodbridge, CT (map)

Madafeh/Open House - Gaza Month 4 - Our Guest: Folk Singer David Rovics.

Please click the above underlined title of the event for more information and to go to the registration page.

Please join us for conversation and songs about Gaza with singer/songwriter David Rovics, who will join us virtually through Zoom from Portland, Oregon.
